data.description: This incredible property was built in 2018 and has been meticulously cared for since then. From the moment you pull up, you'll appreciate the attention to detail that has gone into this home. The curb appeal is undeniable with its perfect mix of stone and brick. Once you walk in, you'll be blown away by the open floor plan and high-end finishes. The kitchen features granite countertops, a huge kitchen island, and stainless steel appliances. You'll love cooking in this kitchen! There's plenty of room for everyone to gather around the island or table. The main level offers an oversized primary suite with a walk-in closet, dual sinks, a soaking tub, and a walk-in shower. There are 2 additional bedrooms and an office with French doors and bow window that lets in a ton of natural light. The upper level offers an additional primary suite option with a walk-in shower. This space can also be used for a media, game, or exercise area. You're going to love living in this home.
